---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services | AresForge">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <h1>Services</h1>
    <p>Engineering solutions built for the age of AI. We handle the complexity so you can focus on what matters.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="services-list">
    <div class="service-item">
      <div class="service-icon">⚡</div>
      <div class="service-content">
        <h2>AI Workflow Automation</h2>
        <p>We design and deploy intelligent agent pipelines that eliminate manual, repetitive work across your business operations. From data processing to customer follow-ups, your workflows run themselves.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Custom agent design and deployment</li>
          <li>Multi-step workflow automation</li>
          <li>Integration with existing tools and platforms</li>
          <li>Ongoing monitoring and optimization</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="service-item">
      <div class="service-icon">🧠</div>
      <div class="service-content">
        <h2>Context Persistence & Agent Memory</h2>
        <p>AI agents lose context between sessions — we fix that. Our context persistence layer keeps your agents aligned across reboots, model switches, and long-running workflows. No more starting from scratch.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Session state management</li>
          <li>Cross-agent context sharing</li>
          <li>Memory architecture design</li>
          <li>Works with Claude, GPT, and custom models</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="service-item">
      <div class="service-icon">🔗</div>
      <div class="service-content">
        <h2>API & Integration Development</h2>
        <p>We connect your tools, platforms, and AI systems into one seamless operational layer. If it has an API, we can make it talk to everything else you use.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>REST and GraphQL API development</li>
          <li>Third-party platform integrations</li>
          <li>Webhook and event-driven architectures</li>
          <li>Legacy system modernization</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="service-item">
      <div class="service-icon">🛠️</div>
      <div class="service-content">
        <h2>Custom Software Development</h2>
        <p>Bespoke full-stack engineering tailored to your exact requirements. From MVPs to production systems, we build software that scales with your business.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Full-stack web application development</li>
          <li>MVP scoping and delivery</li>
          <li>Code review and technical consulting</li>
          <li>System architecture design</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-strip">
    <h2>Not sure which service fits?</h2>
    <p>Let's talk. We'll figure out exactly what you need.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="cta">Book a Free Consultation</a>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 2rem 3rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }
  .page-hero p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .services-list {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 2rem 5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .service-item {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .service-item:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }

  .service-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 48px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .service-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .service-content p {
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .service-content ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .service-content ul li {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .service-content ul li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .service-item { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  }
</style>